dct_title_s: Caerte van't Scheldt ende Santvliet ... door C.J. Visscher. 1640
dct_description_sm: Title cartouche with sleepy fisherman above; ship tracks marked, detailed ships, topography, soldiers, on this large scale map; watermark.
Appears in "Germania Inferior ... Kaert boeck van de XVII. Nederlandtsche Provincien ... Door C. Beudeker." Band 1. No. 18.
